<h2>What are cookies?</h2>

<p>
    Cookies are small text files that are stored on your computer or mobile device
    when you visit a website. They allow the website to remember your actions and preferences
    (such as login, language, font size, and other display preferences) over a period of time,
    so you don't have to keep re-entering them whenever you come back to the site or browse from
    one page to another.
</p>

